Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是三增峠山的山脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于要真正的挑战登山了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过大家为什么对目的地要保密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个什么石头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额 是达磨石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不倒翁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,, {\an8}日语中达磨和不倒翁一个念法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那它上面写着什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梵字aaH 是指大日如来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像写了什么哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山上没有垃圾箱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:18.57,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(628,412)} {\an8}登山这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增峠标高是多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是1786米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高尾山好像是599米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是它的3倍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 但是 这路比想象中更容易走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且到处都有长凳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 长凳是不是太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会很容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要看？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看 从那棵分成两股的树干中间看的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有美丽的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 快走吧 太阳要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我们加紧吧 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前路漫漫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 大家突然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 就像近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 能看到日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次要爬的山决定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 这是惊喜？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我之前说想看富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 你在干什么呢 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之装作不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得日向为我计划了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定这前面还会有更棒的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下马点？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,, {\an8}山路变得险阻 必须从所乘之马上下来的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马还能到这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马儿 真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坡好像陡起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪说马也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斜坡很陡 全是岩石很难走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息的时间变得越来越长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶快跟上大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚也痛 背包也沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难受 我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会来这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在长凳上休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才还有那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一个都没了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 是不是太努力了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:06:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也难怪 毕竟有奖品富士山在等着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经注意到惊喜是什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还为了日向装作没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是这么温柔的小葵也想回家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山呢 和马拉松一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度提高得太快 马上就会累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要保持速度 累了就休息一会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃点甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累的时候甜食最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先掰开放进袋子里 马上就可以吃到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会制造垃圾 很方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 不愧是枫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息完恢复精神再继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢的按照自己的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步幅小一点比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是苦着脸大家都会扫兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 所以枫一直都是面带笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有点勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然开始爬真正的大山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当辛苦的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 要不要试试用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是折叠滑雪杖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个呢 这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对在山路上保持平衡也很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步幅变小 每走一步都要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山呢 虽然一开始在森林里什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登啊登啊 穿过森林的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定有美丽的景色在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那个的时候 我总是在想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没放弃真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没在等你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能只是走的太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来不要急 慢慢走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写的是八十八大师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狂野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵也喝喝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从树缝间透过的阳光非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还是很难走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过感觉很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想快点向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是不能急 要慢慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山崖？要通过这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下去的话绝对没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只看着地面走走看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像日向说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看周围 只看着脚下前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 不怎么害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样应该就能走过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 慢慢走 慢慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步一步向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 已经安全了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 什么事都没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头看看 还是一样的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步一步前行 总能到达的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山 真的像画里一样蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也能看到这样的景色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比照片之类的看起来更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我是一路靠自己的双脚走过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你在路上就注意到惊喜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那个没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚的明白了我为什么要一路走来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了看到这样的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧各位 到山顶还有一点点
